==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Book-learned
<hw>Book"-learned`</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Versed in
books; having knowledge derived from books.</def> <mark>[Often in a
disparaging sense.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Whate'er these <qex>book-learned</qex> blockheads say,⟦br⟧
Solon's the veriest fool in all the play.</q>
<rj><qau>Dryden.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Bookless</ent>⟦br⟧
